headline.print_headline: I Only Miss Last Five Seconds of My Career, Says Bartoli
headline.main: I Only Miss Last Five Seconds of My Career, Says Bartoli

lead_paragraph: Apart from the final five seconds of her Wimbledon singles final last year Marion Bartoli is not missing her tennis career.
